com.paypal.selion.grid.servlets.transfer

Interface UploadResponder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    UploadResponder.AbstractUploadResponder, UploadResponder.JsonUploadResponder, UploadResponder.TextPlainUploadResponder

    public interface UploadResponder
    UploadResponder responds to HTTP POST upload request for any type that extends ManagedArtifact. The response Content-Type is decided by the implementations. The response URLs are REST styled formed after the user Id folder and artifact name. Application folder is inserted if available.

    • Nested Class Summary
